    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu </p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 6 (Spell Level 3)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 4</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 20 | <b>Successes:</b> 3</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 8 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 21</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> S</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You set up a process that converts your body's energy into Chakra upon death. If you die within the duration, your body vanishes over the course of 5 rounds, turning into Chakra and dispersing. This process cannot be reversed in any way once it begins, and does not affect your equipment.<br><br>If performing defensively, you gain a +8 bonus to the Concentration check to do so.</p>\n\n\n\n",
